name: $COOK
description: Launched on November 28, 2023, $COOK is a decentralized cryptocurrency deployed on the Solana blockchain. The project aims to foster a community of WEB3 builders, digital artists, collectors, and investors. With a total token supply of 420,420,690, $COOK is designed to be a community-driven initiative dedicated to enhancing the accessibility and enjoyment of cryptocurrency for a wide audience.
